headline: First Time Business Owners Open New PostalAnnex Location in Northridge, CA
summary: Annex Brands, Inc., one of the leading franchisors in the packing, shipping and office services industries, is proud to announce the opening of its latest PostalAnnex location in Northridge, CA to new owners, Doug and Carolyn Kerzner. This new PostalAnnex is set to offer a wide range of essential shipping, mailbox rental and convenient office services to the local community.
